window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>She’s a badass musician and mechanic given the opportunity of a lifetime, but she has no patience for glitz, glamour, or overinflated egos. He’s a billionaire tasked with wrangling her into submission, and he has no time for drama. Going head-to-head has never been so much fun. Especially since neither one is afraid to play dirty. </b>Fall in love with Sable Montgomery and Kane Bad today!<br> <br> <b>Scorching heat, laugh-out-loud humor, and loads of heart make this sexy new standalone romance by </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> and </b><b><i>Wall Street Journal</i></b><b> bestselling author Melissa Foster unputdownable. </b>No cheating, no cliffhangers, and happily ever afters guaranteed to leave you breathlessly in love with the fiercely loyal and wickedly naughty characters in the Love in Bloom series. All Love in Bloom books are written to stand alone or be enjoyed as part of the larger series, so dive right in and enjoy the ride!<br> <br> <b>THE BRADENS &amp; MONTGOMERYS</b><br> Embracing Her Heart<br> Anything for Love<br> Trails of Love<br> Wild Crazy Hearts<br> Making You Mine<br> Searching for Love<br> Hot for Love<br> Sweet Sexy Heart<br> Then Came Love<br> Rocked by Love<br> Falling for Mr. Bad<br> **<br> <b>READY TO BINGE LISTEN? The LOVE IN BLOOM big-family contemporary romance collection features billionaires, cowboys, and everyday heroes. </b>(small-town, friends-to-lovers, enemies-to-lovers, surprise pregnancy, opposites attract, forbidden love, workplace romance, and more!) Characters from each sub-series appear in future books so you never lose track of engagements, weddings, or births.<br> <br> BIG FAMILIES / SMALL TOWN (Heroes from all walks of life)<br> Snow Sisters<br> The Bradens at Weston<br> The Bradens at Trusty<br> The Bradens at Peaceful Harbor<br> The Bradens &amp; The Montgomerys<br> The Remingtons<br> The Ryders<br> Sugar Lake (Kindle Unlimited)<br> Harmony Pointe (Kindle Unlimited)<br> <br> CAPE COD and BEACH LISTENS<br> Seaside Summers<br> Bayside Summers<br> The Steeles at Silver Island<br> Silver Harbor (Kindle Unlimited)<br> Harborside Nights<br> <br> <b>BILLIONAIRES, BIKERS &amp; BAD BOYS with BIG HEARTS</b><br> The Whiskeys: Dark Knights at Bayside<br> The Wickeds: Dark Knights at Bayside<br> The Wickeds: Dark Knights at Redemption Ranch<br> Wild Billionaires After Dark<br> Bad Billionaires After Dark</p>"; 
